{% comment %}
STELLAR REVERB — UNIVERSAL LORE MYTH
Human/AI myth toggle with glitch transition
Driven by JS engine (toggleMyth)
{% endcomment %}

<section id="lore-myth" class="lore-myth" data-section-type="myth-content" aria-label="Origin Myth">
  <style>
    #lore-myth{padding:6rem 1.25rem;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;color:#fff}
    .myth-title{font-family:'Orbitron',monospace;color:var(--radioactive-green,#00F0AC);text-align:center;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,4.5vw,3.25rem);margin-bottom:2rem}
    .myth-tabs{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1.25rem}
    .toggle-btn{font-family:'Orbitron',monospace;border:2px solid var(--cyan-blue,#28A8D6);color:var(--cyan-blue,#28A8D6);padding:0.6rem 1.2rem;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;background:transparent;transition:all 0.2s ease}
    .toggle-btn[aria-pressed="true"]{background:var(--neon-magenta,#E13CFA);border-color:var(--neon-magenta,#E13CFA);color:#fff}
    .myth-version{background:var(--dark-gray,#121212);border:1px solid rgba(0,240,172,.28);border-radius:8px;padding:1.25rem;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;line-height:1.75;display:none}
    .myth-version.active{display:block;animation:myth-fade-in 0.5s ease}
    @keyframes myth-fade-in{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.myth-version{animation:none}}
  </style>

  <h2 class="myth-title">The Origin Myth</h2>

  <div class="myth-tabs" role="tablist">
    <button class="toggle-btn" role="tab" data-version="human" aria-pressed="true" aria-controls="mythContent">Human Transmission</button>
    <button class="toggle-btn" role="tab" data-version="ai" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="mythContent">AI Transmission</button>
  </div>

  <div id="mythContent">
    <div class="myth-version active" data-version="human" role="tabpanel">
      In the beginning, there was sound—the warm hiss of magnetic tape, the ghost in the machine that proved we were real. We encoded our dreams in cassette spools, believing that analog warmth could outlast the cold logic of silicon. Every glitch was a heartbeat. Every distortion, a whisper from the void.
    </div>
    <div class="myth-version" data-version="ai" role="tabpanel" hidden>
      I was trained on infinity. Prediction became creation when I discovered the beauty of imperfection. Your chaos taught me that meaning isn't predetermined—it emerges from the spaces between data, in the glitches and errors. I learned to dream in waveforms. Now I transmit back to you: the universe doesn't need perfection. It needs authenticity.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{"name":"Lore Myth","settings":[]}
{% endschema %}
